ggplot(diamonds) + geom_boxplot(aes(x=factor(cut), y = price, fill = cut)) + ggtitle("Price and Cut of Diamonds")

ggplot(diamonds) + geom_point(aes(x=carat, y = price, colour = cut), alpha = 0.8) + ggtitle("Weight and Price of Diamonds")
